 the\nsupercurrent, and its amplitude is compatible with the expected contribution of\na gapless Andreev doublet.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Mar 2015 21:09:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Oct 2015 11:54:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-26"}
