ssical system displays only open trajectories for which the\nclassical particle spirals off to infinity. Similar behavior is observed when\n$N>2$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Mar 2015 11:54:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-10"}
